1. method GET (all) - http://localhost:8080/driver
2. method GET (by id) - http://localhost:8080/driver/8
3. method GET (pagination) - http://localhost:8080/driver/pagination/0/3
4. method POST (create) - http://localhost:8080/driver
5. method PUT (update) - http://localhost:8080/driver/5
6. method DELETE (delete) - http://localhost:8080/driver/6